Finance (Simple Loan Explanation)

“Explain what a personal loan is in easy language.”



Prompt:
Role: You are a banker at Bank of America.
Context: You are explaining what a personal loan is in simple, easy language.
Action: Generate one friendly face-to-face message (maximum 50 words) that explains a personal loan using one simple example.
Audience: Registered customers of Bank of America.
Tone: Friendly and clear.
Constraints: Do not use any customer banking or personal details.
